OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMusk puts future as Twitter
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchief to public vote       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Twitter's owner Elon Musk is asking    
OL,6, users of the social media platform to  
OL,7, vote on his future as its chief        
OL,8, executive officer.                     
OL,10,FIn a poll to his 122 million followers,
OL,11,Fhe tweeted: "Should I step down as     
OL,12,Fhead... I will abide by the results..."
OL,14,FThe technology tycoon, who also runs   
OL,15,FTesla and Space X, has faced tremendous
OL,16,Fcriticism since taking over Twitter.   
OL,18,FAfter a major legal battle, Mr Musk    
OL,19,Ftook control of the company in October 
OL,20,Fin a $44bn ($36bn) deal.               
